'''布萊頓市政廳'''（{{lang-en|Brighton Town Hall}}）位於[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[東薩塞克斯郡|東薩塞克斯郡]][[布萊頓|布萊頓]]的巴多羅買廣場，於1830年提出興建並於1832年建成。此市政廳用以取代舊市政廳，並同樣設有警察局拘留室<ref name=old-police-cells-brighton-town-hall>{{cite web|url=http://www.oldpolicecellsmuseum.org.uk/page_id__472_path__0p303p.aspx|title=Brighton Town Hall|publisher=The Old Police Cells Museum|last=Beaken|first=Paul|accessdate=2013-10-12|archive-date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012102441/http://www.oldpolicecellsmuseum.org.uk/page_id__472_path__0p303p.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.british-history.ac.uk/report.aspx?compid=56961|title=A History of the County of Sussex: Volume 7, THE BOROUGH OF BRIGHTON|author=Louis Francis Salzman|accessdate=2013-10-12|archive-date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012081500/http://www.british-history.ac.uk/report.aspx?compid=56961|dead-url=no}}</ref>，拘留室一直使用至1967年，現已開放為舊拘留室博物館（Old Police Cells Museum）<ref name=old-police-cells-brighton-town-hall/>。[[布萊頓和霍夫|布萊頓和霍夫]]市議會的註冊辦事處亦設在此市政廳<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.brighton-hove.gov.uk/a-z/register-office|title=Register Office|publisher=Brighton and Hove City Council|accessdate=2013-10-12|archive-date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012195345/http://www.brighton-hove.gov.uk/a-z/register-office|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

